translation.Message_0_Page_0: You've done very well, <color=rare>Lieutenant <name_char></color>. With this threat eliminated, we can focus on retaking Moneypoint.
translation.Message_0_Page_1: In other words, we've recently acquired a device from one of the former military bases, with some ammo of course, that we have agreed to pass on to you as a "thanks" for helping our cause.
